'''Shuban''' : Shubanku waa kordhidda tirada iyo 
jilicsanaanta saxarada.  Taas oo kala ahaan karta 
in badan oo jilicsan ama fudud ilaa in badan oo 
biyo-biyo ah.  Hal ama laba mar oo ah In yar oo 
jilicsan ma aha shuban, mana u baahna 
daaweyn.  
Shubanka waxaa inta badan keena xanuun 
feyras ah ama cunidda cunto aanay calooshu 
oggolayn.  Haddii shubanka cunuggaagu uu 
keenay bakteeriya, dulin, ama feyras khaas ah, 
eeg warqadda barashada, “Kaartada tixraaca 
shubanka.” 
